description: This Chainlink VRF top 9% rating Yulenka purrs with a rating of 75, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 75, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 2 for East, 8 for South, and Box for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/80751-12844-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
